entry.string: INSERT INTO BI_REPORTS.DBO.T_FACT_ROOM_REVENUE_SALES(HotelID, DateID, ContractID, HotelRoomID, StaffID, UpsellRoomRev, ValueAddedRev) VALUES(#[payload.Hotelid],#[payload.DateID],#[payload.ContractID],#[payload.HotelRoomID],#[payload.staffid],#[payload.UpsellRoomRev],#[payload.ValueAddedRev])

SELECT dtl.HotelID,dtl.StaffID, CONVERT(INT, CAST (ExtractDate as DATETIME)) as dateid, el.Offering_Category,avg(el.offrngScore) as offrngScore,sum(dtl.RoomRev) as RoomRev,el.offering_id FROM ( SELECT A.hotelid,A.ExtractDate , Max(D.contractstartdate) AS ContractStartDate, Max(D.contractenddate) AS ContractEndDate, A.staffid as staffid, sum (A.upsellroomrev) as RoomRev
FROM TSA_APS.DBO.T_TRN_APSCACHEDUPSELL A Inner Join TSA_APS.DBO.T_TRN_HOTELROOM Room on occroomtype=Room.roomcode and A.hotelid=Room.hotelid and effectivedate>= (select max(effectivedate) from TSA_APS.DBO.T_TRN_HOTELROOM where hotelid=A.hotelid) Inner JOIN TSA_APS.DBO.T_TRN_HOTELCONTRACTDETAILS D ON A.hotelid = D.hotelid AND A.Extractdate BETWEEN D.contractstartdate AND D.contractenddate GROUP BY A.hotelid,ExtractDate,Staffid ) dtl inner join ( Select t.StaffID,t.Hotelcode,t.offering_id,t.offrngScore,t.status_desc,t.Offering_Type,t.Offering_Category,t.locale_id from UAT_FACT_ELEARNING t ) el on dtl.staffid = el.StaffID inner join T_MAS_HOTEL ht on el.Hotelcode = REPLACE(LEFT(ht.HotelCode, CHARINDEX('~',ht.HotelCode)-1),'_',' ') and dtl.HotelID = ht.HotelID --where dtl.HotelID =271 group by dtl.HotelID,dtl.StaffID,el.Offering_Category,ExtractDate,el.offering_id

SELECT A.Hotelid, CONVERT(INT, CAST (A.ExtractDate as DATETIME)) as DateID, max(D.rowID) as ContractID, room.rowid as HotelRoomID, A.staffid, sum (A.upsellroomrev) as UpsellRoomRev, sum (A.upsellroomrevvalue) as ValueAddedRev FROM TSA_APS.DBO.T_TRN_APSCACHEDUPSELL A Inner Join TSA_APS.DBO.T_TRN_HOTELROOM Room on occroomtype=Room.roomcode and A.hotelid=Room.hotelid and effectivedate>= (select max(effectivedate) from T_TRN_HOTELROOM where hotelid=A.hotelid) Inner JOIN TSA_APS.DBO.T_TRN_HOTELCONTRACTDETAILS D ON A.hotelid = D.hotelid AND A.Extractdate BETWEEN D.contractstartdate AND D.contractenddate WHERE D.CONTRACTSTARTDATE >= '2015-01-01' group by A.hotelid,RoomGrp,A.ExtractDate,Staffid,room.rowid

SELECT dtl.HotelID,dtl.StaffID, e.Offering_Category,avg(e.offrngScore),sum(dtl.RoomRev) as RoomRev,e.status_desc from ( SELECT A.hotelid,A.period, Max(D.contractstartdate) AS ContractStartDate, Max(D.contractenddate) AS ContractEndDate, A.staffid as staffid, sum (A.upsellroomrev) as RoomRev FROM T_TRN_APSCACHEDUPSELL A Inner Join T_TRN_HOTELROOM Room on occroomtype=Room.roomcode and A.hotelid=Room.hotelid and effectivedate>= (select max(effectivedate) from T_TRN_HOTELROOM where hotelid=A.hotelid) Inner JOIN T_TRN_HOTELCONTRACTDETAILS D ON A.hotelid = D.hotelid AND A.Extractdate BETWEEN D.contractstartdate AND D.contractenddate --WHERE A.HotelID =271 GROUP BY A.hotelid,Period,Staffid ) dtl inner join ( Select t.StaffID,t.Hotelcode,t.offering_id,t.offrngScore,t.status_desc,t.Offering_Type,t.Offering_Category,t.locale_id
from UAT_FACT_ELEARNING t )e on dtl.staffid = e.StaffID inner join T_MAS_HOTEL ht on e.Hotelcode = REPLACE(LEFT(ht.HotelCode, CHARINDEX('~',ht.HotelCode)-1),'_',' ') and dtl.HotelID = ht.HotelID --where dtl.HotelID =271 group by dtl.HotelID,dtl.StaffID,e.Offering_Category,e.status_desc,Period

SELECT dtl.HotelID,dtl.StaffID, CONVERT(INT, CAST (ExtractDate as DATETIME)) as dateid, el.Offering_Category,avg(el.offrngScore) as offrngScore,sum(dtl.RoomRev) as RoomRev,el.offering_id FROM ( SELECT A.hotelid,A.ExtractDate , Max(D.contractstartdate) AS ContractStartDate, Max(D.contractenddate) AS ContractEndDate, A.staffid as staffid, sum (A.upsellroomrev) as RoomRev
FROM TSA_APS.DBO.T_TRN_APSCACHEDUPSELL A Inner Join TSA_APS.DBO.T_TRN_HOTELROOM Room on occroomtype=Room.roomcode and A.hotelid=Room.hotelid and effectivedate>= (select max(effectivedate) from TSA_APS.DBO.T_TRN_HOTELROOM where hotelid=A.hotelid) Inner JOIN TSA_APS.DBO.T_TRN_HOTELCONTRACTDETAILS D ON A.hotelid = D.hotelid AND A.Extractdate BETWEEN D.contractstartdate AND D.contractenddate GROUP BY A.hotelid,ExtractDate,Staffid ) dtl inner join ( Select t.StaffID,t.Hotelcode,t.offering_id,t.offrngScore,t.status_desc,t.Offering_Type,t.Offering_Category,t.locale_id from UAT_FACT_ELEARNING t ) el on dtl.staffid = el.StaffID inner join T_MAS_HOTEL ht on el.Hotelcode = REPLACE(LEFT(ht.HotelCode, CHARINDEX('~',ht.HotelCode)-1),'_',' ') and dtl.HotelID = ht.HotelID --where dtl.HotelID =271 group by dtl.HotelID,dtl.StaffID,el.Offering_Category,ExtractDate,el.offering_id

SELECT dtl.HotelID,dtl.StaffID, e.Offering_Category,avg(e.offrngScore) as offrngScore,sum(dtl.RoomRev) as RoomRev,e.status_desc from ( SELECT A.hotelid,A.period, Max(D.contractstartdate) AS ContractStartDate, Max(D.contractenddate) AS ContractEndDate, A.staffid as staffid, sum (A.upsellroomrev) as RoomRev FROM T_TRN_APSCACHEDUPSELL A Inner Join T_TRN_HOTELROOM Room on occroomtype=Room.roomcode and A.hotelid=Room.hotelid and effectivedate>= (select max(effectivedate) from T_TRN_HOTELROOM where hotelid=A.hotelid) Inner JOIN T_TRN_HOTELCONTRACTDETAILS D ON A.hotelid = D.hotelid AND A.Extractdate BETWEEN D.contractstartdate AND D.contractenddate --WHERE A.HotelID =271 GROUP BY A.hotelid,Period,Staffid ) dtl inner join ( Select t.StaffID,t.Hotelcode,t.offering_id,t.offrngScore,t.status_desc,t.Offering_Type,t.Offering_Category,t.locale_id
from UAT_FACT_ELEARNING t )e on dtl.staffid = e.StaffID inner join T_MAS_HOTEL ht on e.Hotelcode = REPLACE(LEFT(ht.HotelCode, CHARINDEX('~',ht.HotelCode)-1),'_',' ') and dtl.HotelID = ht.HotelID --where dtl.HotelID =271 group by dtl.HotelID,dtl.StaffID,e.Offering_Category,e.status_desc,Period

SELECT ROWID AS HotelRoomID, RoomCode AS RoomCode, RoomName AS RoomName, RoomGrp AS RoomGrp, RoomCategory AS RoomCategory, NoRoom AS NoRoom, NULL AS OccupiedRoom, null as VacantRoom FROM TSA_APS.DBO.T_TRN_HOTELROOM

SELECT dtl.HotelID,dtl.StaffID, e.Offering_Category,avg(e.offrngScore),sum(dtl.RoomRev) as RoomRev,e.status_desc from ( SELECT A.hotelid,A.period, Max(D.contractstartdate) AS ContractStartDate, Max(D.contractenddate) AS ContractEndDate, A.staffid as staffid, sum (A.upsellroomrev) as RoomRev FROM T_TRN_APSCACHEDUPSELL A Inner Join T_TRN_HOTELROOM Room on occroomtype=Room.roomcode and A.hotelid=Room.hotelid and effectivedate>= (select max(effectivedate) from T_TRN_HOTELROOM where hotelid=A.hotelid) Inner JOIN T_TRN_HOTELCONTRACTDETAILS D ON A.hotelid = D.hotelid AND A.Extractdate BETWEEN D.contractstartdate AND D.contractenddate --WHERE A.HotelID =271 GROUP BY A.hotelid,Period,Staffid ) dtl inner join ( Select t.StaffID,t.Hotelcode,t.offering_id,t.offrngScore,t.status_desc,t.Offering_Type,t.Offering_Category,t.locale_id
from UAT_FACT_ELEARNING t )e on dtl.staffid = e.StaffID inner join T_MAS_HOTEL ht on e.Hotelcode = REPLACE(LEFT(ht.HotelCode, CHARINDEX('~',ht.HotelCode)-1),'_',' ') and dtl.HotelID = ht.HotelID --where dtl.HotelID =271 group by dtl.HotelID,dtl.StaffID,e.Offering_Category,e.status_desc,Period

SELECT ROWID AS HotelRoomID,RoomCode AS RoomCode,RoomName AS RoomName,RoomGrp AS RoomGrp,RoomCategory AS RoomCategory, NoRoom AS NoRoom,NULL AS OccupiedRoom,null as VacantRoom FROM TSA_APS.DBO.T_TRN_HOTELROOM where hotelid in (1137 ,287 ,1519 ,2588 ,2588 ,2588 ,2588)
